Datensatzklasse TypeCount

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
org.com.model.records.TypeCount
Datensatzkomponenten:
movie - The count of movies.
series - The count of series.
anime - The count of anime.
public record TypeCount(int movie, int series, int anime) extends Record
A record representing the count of different types of cinematics.

This record is used to store the number of movies, series, and anime for analytics or display purposes in the application.

Version:
1.0
Autor:
umut
